(118, 'Fahed Shehab', 'Artist and graphic designer..', 'fahed.pg@gmail.com', 1, 'profiles/profile_118.jpg', NULL, 'heroes/hero_118.jpg', 'Fahad Shehab, a Palestinian from Gaza, uses art, color, sound, and movement to capture and communicate with the world.He developed his skills through workshops in Palestinian institutions, gaining a community dimension that informed his human artistic work .He has participated in various competitions and events, receiving the Czech Humanity Lady Award and being nominated in the Ismail Shamout Artist Competition. His journey as a human medicine student and artist is shaped by culture, using art', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 26, 0, 1, NULL, '$2y$12$Tfekkkj4Z.Qax8sFUTJtD.LFAYr2jojal1j9kQw42mXjjxf898w76', NULL, '2025-12-09 12:01:36', '2026-02-20 01:41:37', 'Fahed', 'Shehab', 'Designer', 'Visual Arts', 'Fahed', 'Artist and graphic designer..', '0597865774', 'PS', 'Gaza', 'Alremal street', '10+', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
