(66, 76, 'hidden story', 'Hidden story is a fashion project that reveals the unseen layers of  womanhood the strength beneath softness the resilience behind , and the beauty that remains untouched even through loss.\r\nthrough sculpted cuts emotional detailing and symbolic craftsmanship the collection celebrated women who carry hidden battels with grace  inspired by my mother\'s journey this project redefines femineity as power , depth and story that lives beneath the surface.', 'fashion design', '', NULL, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 11:15:19', 194, '2025-12-01 11:54:08', '2026-02-05 02:15:08', 1),
(67, 76, 'MeloMe', 'MeloMe is a wearable design created for children aged 3-6 with Autism Spectrum Disorder, helping them self-regulate during moments of sensory overload. The piece is a deep-pressure compression undershirt, made with stretchable fabrics and strategically placed tension bands that provide a calming sense of containment, reducing the likelihood of emotional meltdowns. Developed in collaboration with Alpha Center for Autism, the design is grounded in real needs and supported by professional insights.', 'Fashion design', '', NULL, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 11:15:19', 194, '2025-12-01 11:54:08', '2026-02-19 11:21:10', 21),
(68, 79, 'Iqra Bookshelf', 'A bespoke wooden bookshelf inspired by Arabic calligraphy, featuring the word “Iqra” (اقرأ, meaning “Read”) as part of its structure. This piece merges functional storage with artistic design, serving as both a statement décor item and a practical bookshelf. Made of high-quality', 'Furniture / Bookshelf', 'products/9496bf5d-56bc-45d4-8b7e-8dddcd8fce77.jpeg', NULL, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 11:15:19', 194, '2025-12-02 11:51:55', '2026-01-31 04:21:52', 13),
(69, 79, 'Interior woodwork', 'Precision-cut wooden window sill made from high-quality timber. Provides a durable and stylish surface for windows, complementing interior décor with a warm, natural wood finish', 'Woodwork', 'products/ee308113-437d-43f9-bb16-7ef6184b99b2.jpeg', NULL, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 11:15:19', 194, '2025-12-02 11:51:55', '2026-02-05 18:35:31', 14),
(70, 79, 'Tree Shelf', 'A handcrafted shelf inspired by the organic shape of a tree, made from premium oak wood. Perfect for displaying books, plants, or decorative items, this piece adds a natural, artistic touch to any interior space.', 'Interior Woodwork / Shelves / Tree Shelves', 'products/7f1b6c3a-7d21-45a1-b4a4-44f9173376ea.jpeg', NULL, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 11:15:19', 194, '2025-12-02 11:51:55', '2026-02-17 11:09:04', 4),
(71, 80, 'دوار المعلم- البيرة', 'This piece is a collaboration with Wasel Artworks and the artist Jasem Shoman. The Calligraphy is designed by Wasel, and the whole artwork is designed by the artist Jasem. My job in this project is to connect the letters on the different faces of the artwork so that it is readable seamlessly through any face. We used different techniques to come to this result. It was a great experience that I learned so much from.', 'Artwork', 'products/e66c3332-474f-4b7c-aa7c-9c5343c44fd6.jpg', NULL, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 11:15:19', 194, '2025-12-02 12:57:08', '2026-02-12 08:35:47', 15),
