(219, 157, 'Social media Ads', 'This collection showcases O2 Restaurant\'s bold red visual identity. The designs highlight modern solutions for Gaza\'s needs, such as delivery services covering the Middle Area (Nuseirat, Deir al-Balah, etc.), and innovative electric shawarma grilling to bypass gas shortages. It also promotes digital payments via PalPay for customer convenience. Unified by the O2 logo and a clear red-and-white theme, the brand focuses on speed, reliability, and practical lifestyle solutions.', 'Designing', '', NULL, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 11:13:15', 194, '2025-12-17 10:59:38', '2026-02-20 04:27:35', 45),
(220, 157, 'Socia media Ads', 'The Abu Humaid Nuts collection features a unified identity linking products to health and vitality. Designs highlight benefits like heart health, physical strength, and variety through nature-inspired green themes. Using simple visuals and interactive styles, it shifts the brand from selling a product to promoting a healthy lifestyle. Clear messaging and professional layouts establish a trustworthy, wellness-focused brand.', 'Other', '', NULL, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 11:12:31', 194, '2025-12-17 10:59:38', '2026-02-19 22:43:08', 25),
(221, 157, 'Arbiton Brand Identity', 'The Arbiton identity brilliantly fuses legal and industrial themes by integrating \"justice scales\" within a \"gear\". The bold blue and energetic orange palette reflects trust and industrial vitality. With a modern Sans Serif font and consistent patterns, the design ensures a professional, high-authority look across all digital and print platforms.', 'Other', '', NULL, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 11:13:15', 194, '2025-12-17 10:59:38', '2026-02-13 15:32:04', 24),
(222, 157, 'Sand Timer Set', 'The UAE-based Fun Learning store offers the \"Smart Skills\" Sand Timer Set, an innovative educational tool featuring 6 colorful timers ranging from 1 to 30 minutes. Designed for children aged 4+, it enhances time management and focus through safe, interactive play. The packaging reflects a modern visual identity that balances fun with learning, aligning with the store’s mission to provide tools that build self-discipline and \"make every second count\".', 'Glass Products', '', NULL, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 11:13:15', 194, '2025-12-17 10:59:38', '2026-01-19 12:09:53', 4),
(223, 157, 'Company profile', 'These company profiles feature professional layouts across food, real estate, and service sectors. The food profile uses vibrant yellow and white to highlight products, while the engineering profile adopts a minimalist blue and grey theme for a premium feel. Utilizing high-quality mockups, the designs balance imagery and text to ensure a clean, professional, and readable presentation for any business.', 'Designing', '', NULL, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 11:13:15', 194, '2025-12-17 10:59:38', '2026-02-18 21:44:16', 18),
