(247, 164, 'Storage Systems', 'Our storage systems furniture combines functionality, durability, and modern design to help you organize any space efficiently. Ideal for offices, schools, or commercial environments, these solutions include cabinets, shelves, lockers, and modular units crafted from high-quality materials. Designed for easy access, optimal space utilization, and long-lasting performance, our storage systems keep your environment tidy and well-organized while complementing your interior style.', 'Furniture', '', NULL, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 11:12:08', 194, '2025-12-22 12:28:59', '2026-02-15 09:26:32', 11),
(248, 164, 'Chair Series', 'Our Chair Collection offers seating solutions for every need. Executive and operational chairs provide ergonomic comfort for offices. Visitor chairs are stylish and durable for guests. Wooden chairs combine classic design with quality craftsmanship. Stools offer compact, versatile seating, while multipurpose chairs adapt to various spaces. All are made with high-quality materials for lasting comfort, durability, and style.', 'Furniture', '', NULL, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 11:12:08', 194, '2025-12-22 12:28:59', '2026-02-16 05:01:57', 2),
