(269, 175, 'Living Room Seating / Sofa', 'A single sofa — also known as a 1‑seater sofa or sofa chair — is a compact upholstered seating piece designed to offer the comfort and style of a full sofa in a smaller footprint, perfect for individual relaxation spots, cozy corners, reading nooks, bedrooms, or living rooms. It combines the cushioning and design of a traditional sofa with a space‑saving structure that fits well in both small and large interiors', 'Sofas & Seating', '', NULL, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 11:12:08', 194, '2025-12-23 10:29:43', '2026-02-05 12:05:44', 9),
