(87, 103, 9, 'CUBE MASTER – Corporate Visual Identity', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:17', 194, 0, 42, 0, '2025-12-05 06:15:14', '2026-02-18 18:52:59', 'I developed the full digital visual system for CUBE MASTER, including brand identity elements, character-based key visuals, social media layouts and website UI screens. My role covered creative direction, visual storytelling and designing a modern tech-focused style that reflects the company’s expertise in Odoo, AWS and cloud solutions.', 'Lead Designer – Brand Identity & Visual System', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(88, 103, 9, '7th Dimension Office for Architecture – Company Profile Design', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:17', 194, 0, 23, 0, '2025-12-05 06:15:14', '2026-02-19 16:33:02', 'Designed the printed company profile for 7th Dimension Office for Architecture, including layout, typography, iconography and image treatment. I created a clean, architecture-focused visual style and organized the content to clearly present the firm’s history, services, vision and projects in a professional, easy-to-read format.', 'Lead Graphic Designer – Layout & Brand Implementation', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(89, 103, 9, 'gig Kuwait Insurance – Social Media Campaign Design', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:17', 194, 0, 3, 0, '2025-12-05 06:15:14', '2026-02-04 02:08:30', 'Designed a series of social media posts for gig Kuwait, focusing on family, car and travel insurance. I created 3D-inspired key visuals, compositions and layouts tailored for Instagram, ensuring clear messaging in Arabic, strong product highlighting and a consistent visual style across the whole campaign.', 'Lead Social Media & Visual Designer', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(90, 103, 9, 'National Center for Strategic Companies – Website UI Design', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:17', 194, 0, 33, 0, '2025-12-05 06:15:14', '2026-02-19 11:36:17', 'Designed the full website interface for the National Center for Strategic Companies in Saudi Arabia, covering homepage layout, service sections, partner showcases, e-learning modules and registration flows. I developed a clean Arabic UI with strong visual hierarchy, modern icons and smooth navigation to present the center’s programs, digital services and strategic initiatives.', 'Lead UI/UX & Web Designer', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(91, 103, 9, 'Edustores – Study Abroad Platform Website UI', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:17', 194, 0, 18, 0, '2025-12-05 06:15:14', '2026-02-18 07:21:16', 'Designed a website interface for Edustores, an education and study-abroad platform based in Türkiye. I created the main landing page with a hero section featuring a student on campus and interactive cards for accredited universities and partners. The design focuses on clarity, trust and an intuitive journey for students exploring programs and services.', 'Lead UI/UX Designer', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(93, 110, 9, 'مطبخ عصري', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:10', 194, 0, 16, 0, '2025-12-07 11:12:10', '2026-02-19 22:57:18', 'مطبخ عصري كامل التصميم مصنوع من خشب متين مع تشطيبات عالية الجودة، يشمل خزائن علوية وسفلية، مساحة عمل واسعة، وأسطح مقاومة للخدوش والحرارة. التصميم يجمع بين الجمال والعملية، مع إمكانية اختيار الألوان والتفاصيل حسب مساحة منزلك واحتياجاتك.', 'مطابخ / Kitchens', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
