(173, 75, 9, 'Golden Tower Hotel – Nassar Nassar Building', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:00', 194, 0, 4, 0, '2025-12-28 12:18:11', '2026-02-16 20:48:33', 'Rehabilitation of an Existing office building to be utilized as a hotel of 83\r\nroom with all facilities\r\nABB as the main Contracted Consultant prepared the full package of the\r\nrenovation works also Architect Anton Stephan was the main designer of\r\nthe building during his work with the Architectural and Engineering office', 'Other', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(174, 75, 9, 'Carthage MP Hall', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:00', 194, 0, 3, 0, '2025-12-28 12:21:36', '2026-01-31 02:49:59', 'Rehabilitating Existing Stone factory into Multi-purpose Hall\r\nSchematic Design, Licensing Drawings, landscape & Interior Design', 'Other', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(175, 75, 9, 'Jad Almasri villa', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:00', 194, 0, 31, 0, '2025-12-28 12:22:51', '2026-02-16 00:05:54', 'Rehabilitation for existing skeleton to be converted into a private villa\r\nSchematic Design, Licensing Drawings, landscape & Interior Design', 'Other', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(184, 113, 9, 'Residential Apartments', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:00', 194, 0, 5, 0, '2025-12-29 11:43:22', '2026-02-04 01:21:49', 'They provide end-to-end solutions for fully furnishing apartments, including living rooms, bedrooms, dining areas, kitchens, and storage solutions. Every piece is crafted with high-quality materials and modern designs, ensuring comfort, functionality, and a cohesive aesthetic throughout the home.', 'Services Provider', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(185, 113, 9, 'Commercial Spaces & Companies', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:00', 194, 0, 8, 0, '2025-12-29 11:43:49', '2026-02-18 23:27:09', 'Hands Furniture also caters to offices, showrooms, and commercial establishments, delivering custom furniture and interior solutions. This includes reception areas, workstations, meeting rooms, display units, and storage systems — all designed to enhance workflow, brand image, and user experience.', 'Services Provider', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(186, 113, 9, 'Luxury Apartments & Villas', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:00', 194, 0, 7, 0, '2025-12-29 11:44:55', '2026-02-20 14:46:00', 'Hands Furniture provides complete furnishing solutions for high-end apartments and villas, including living rooms, bedrooms, kitchens, and dining areas. Each piece is crafted with premium materials and modern designs to ensure elegance, comfort, and a cohesive aesthetic throughout the home.', 'Services Provider', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(187, 113, 9, 'Showrooms & Retail Stores', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:00', 194, 0, 18, 0, '2025-12-29 11:45:26', '2026-02-14 19:08:20', 'Custom display units, shelving, counters, and fixtures are crafted to highlight products while maintaining an attractive and functional retail layout. Every design focuses on both aesthetics and practicality for maximum customer engagement.', 'Services Provider', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(188, 113, 9, 'Hotels & Guesthouses', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:00', 194, 0, 24, 0, '2025-12-29 11:45:48', '2026-02-18 10:03:53', 'From guest rooms to lobbies and conference areas, Hands Furniture offers comprehensive furnishing solutions that combine comfort, elegance, and functionality to enhance the guest experience.', 'Services Provider', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(189, 113, 9, 'Home Renovation Projects', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:00', 194, 0, 21, 0, '2025-12-29 11:46:19', '2026-02-18 07:20:53', 'Custom-built furniture is designed to perfectly match home renovations or expansions, ensuring seamless integration and optimized functionality.', 'Services Provider', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(190, 156, 9, 'Environmental Projects', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:00', 194, 0, 2, 0, '2025-12-30 08:45:11', '2026-01-19 13:27:59', 'Eco-friendly Factory Project\r\nUniversal Mattresses Co has developed an eco-friendly manufacturing system to minimize industrial waste and ensure product safety. Most raw materials are recycled and reused, reducing environmental impact. This initiative has been formalized with the implementation of an environmental management system, earning the company ISO 14001 certification.', 'Other', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(191, 156, 9, 'Employee Transportation & Meal Program', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:00', 194, 0, 5, 0, '2025-12-30 08:45:38', '2026-01-21 05:46:14', 'The company ensures the welfare of its employees by providing daily transportation to and from the factory and offering a daily meal in a spacious, high-standard dining hall. This program enhances staff convenience, satisfaction, and productivity.', 'Other', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(192, 156, 9, 'Labor Compliance & Workplace Standards Project', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:00', 194, 0, 10, 0, '2025-12-30 08:46:18', '2026-02-17 17:06:35', 'Universal Mattresses Co adheres strictly to Palestinian Labor Law No. 7 (2000), as well as international labor agreements and workplace safety standards. This commitment ensures an ethical, legal, and safe work environment for all staff.', 'Other', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(193, 156, 9, 'Special Needs Employment Program', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:00', 194, 0, 2, 0, '2025-12-30 08:46:40', '2026-01-19 13:27:51', 'As part of its social responsibility, the company actively employs people with disabilities in collaboration with the Palestinian National Alliance. This initiative promotes inclusion and integration into the workforce and has earned official recognition and honors for the company.', 'Other', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(194, 156, 9, 'Youth & Student Training Program', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:00', 194, 0, 2, 0, '2025-12-30 08:46:59', '2026-01-19 13:27:58', 'To support young talent and provide practical work experience, Universal Mattresses Co partners with Al-Quds University’s dual studies program. This initiative allows students to gain hands-on experience within the company and is supported by the German government. The company has been formally recognized in official ceremonies for this contribution.', 'Other', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(195, 156, 9, 'Product Range Expansion Project', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:41:00', 194, 0, 2, 0, '2025-12-30 08:47:16', '2026-01-19 13:27:55', 'The company has continually expanded its product portfolio to include diverse, high-quality items such as Zemberk, foam, pocket, and cut-foam mattresses, fully upholstered beds, medical pillows, and seat cushions. Advanced materials like smart foam (Visco), flexible foam (Latex), pocket springs, and specialized fabrics resistant to mold, fire, and moisture are used to meet different customer preferences.', 'Other', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(196, 156, 9, 'Foam Production Line Project (2018)', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:40:54', 194, 0, 5, 0, '2025-12-30 08:47:42', '2026-02-04 03:11:20', 'In 2018, Universal Mattresses Co launched a dedicated foam production line. This project completed the full production cycle for all product types and created additional employment opportunities within the company.', 'Other', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(197, 156, 9, 'Workforce Expansion and Capacity Building', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:40:54', 194, 0, 3, 0, '2025-12-30 08:48:02', '2026-02-04 09:29:40', 'The company currently employs over 250 staff, with plans to increase this number to meet future growth needs. Staff development is emphasized through participation in international trade fairs and continuous training programs for both administrative and production teams, ensuring enhanced skills and expertise.', 'Other', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(198, 156, 9, 'Technology Integration Project', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:40:54', 194, 0, 12, 0, '2025-12-30 08:48:29', '2026-02-17 23:05:51', 'To modernize its operations, Universal Mattresses Co has developed advanced internal administrative and production systems. This ensures greater efficiency, streamlined processes, and alignment with contemporary production and management standards.', 'Other', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(199, 156, 9, 'Quality Management Project', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:40:54', 194, 0, 3, 0, '2025-12-30 08:48:50', '2026-02-04 09:28:18', 'Maintaining high production and operational standards, the company implemented an international quality management system, earning the ISO 9001 certification.', 'Other', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(200, 156, 9, 'Market Expansion Project', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:40:54', 194, 0, 3, 0, '2025-12-30 08:49:11', '2026-02-04 09:31:57', 'Universal Mattresses Co serves both local and Israeli markets and exports part of its production internationally. The company has established multiple branches and sales areas across Palestine to meet customer demand effectively.', 'Other', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(201, 156, 9, 'International Exposure & Industry Development', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:40:54', 194, 0, 4, 0, '2025-12-30 08:49:30', '2026-02-08 08:49:02', 'The company actively participates in international trade fairs to stay updated on the latest industry trends and innovations. This initiative helps maintain competitiveness and ensures continuous development of both production and administrative staff.', 'Other', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(202, 151, 9, 'Pizza Advertising Campaign', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:40:54', 194, 0, 13, 0, '2025-12-31 07:22:48', '2026-02-14 08:39:02', 'مجموعة تصاميم إعلانية لبيتزا، تم تنفيذها بأسلوب بصري جذاب يركز على إبراز المنتج، الألوان الشهية، وتنسيق العناصر لشد انتباه الجمهور وتحفيز الطلب تم الاعتماد على تصميم واضح ورسائل تسويقية بسيطة تناسب وسائل التواصل الاجتماعي', 'Designer', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
(203, 151, 9, 'Ayla Modern School Logo & Stamp Design', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-08 10:40:54', 194, 0, 24, 0, '2025-12-31 07:27:53', '2026-02-14 05:27:12', 'مشروع تصميم هوية بصرية تعليمية لمدرسة إيلا الحديثة، شمل تصميم شعار عصري يعكس القيم التعليمية والتطور الأكاديمي، بالإضافة إلى ختم رسمي يُستخدم في المعاملات والوثائق المدرسية. تم الاعتماد على أسلوب بسيط واحترافي، مع استخدام رموز تعليمية وألوان هادئة تعزز الموثوقية والتميز.', 'Designer', NULL, 0, 0, 0),
