(216, 133, 9, 'Supplying furniture for all security agency headquarters.', '', 0, 'approved', NULL, '2026-01-20 05:04:44', 194, 0, 8, 0, '2026-01-07 08:21:55', '2026-02-18 16:44:06', 'Furniture has been manufactured and supplied to all security agencies across all governorates, in accordance with the required specifications and standards. The work included fully equipping offices and facilities with the necessary furniture, ensuring high quality, precise execution, and timely delivery.', 'Services Provider', 'Furniture supply', 0, 0, 0),
