(346, 243, 'Social Media & Brand Identity Design', 'I create clean and professional social media posts and brand identities for small businesses. My workflow includes AI-assisted tools to explore colors, layouts, and visual concepts efficiently. Each service includes multiple posts or brand elements with one round of revisions to ensure your content looks polished and effective.', 'Graphic Design', 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '2026-02-03 09:57:01', '2026-02-03 09:57:01', 0, 0),
